When Sophie Dahl broke into modelling in 1997, she was the hottest face - and body - of the time.

Under the guidance of Storm, the agency that discovered Kate Moss, Sophie appeared in campaigns for Versace, Alexander McQueen and Patrick Cox.

But two daughters and nearly two decades later, she admits that her life now is worlds away from that scene – and she never really knew what all the fuss was about.

